data.description: Back on the market due to buyer financing! Welcome to your forever home in a newer neighborhood, in close proximity to nearby schools, mountain bike trails, and grocery stores! Into parks? Check out the nearby, dog, splash, and national park. A hop, skip, and a jump from downtown, this 5 year old construction boasts: GRANITE counters, stainless appliances, a fenced exterior dog run, rear yard access for boats/RVs, TWO outdoor sheds/workshops with electrical, up-to-date alarm and security features. All appliances are included except for washer/dryer. X FLOOD ZONE
